{"tid":893494,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實有幾多人搵到一份自己鍾意嘅工，每日都好有動力返工","createTime":"2018-11-07T16:18:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T14:12:43.000Z","uid":169938,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"084387713b84af544c7fdb61de1dbd07f44af5dd","tid":893494,"uid":169938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T16:18:24.000Z","msg":"FG做咗幾個月嘢，覺得而家份工正正常常，但唔會令自己每日都好有動力去返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗轉工又唔知咩適合自己，好冇方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d6fafe65b1ff6017a7fef399bc555fa1b4625e","tid":893494,"uid":5499,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T16:39:15.000Z","msg":"當興趣變成工作，慢慢都會討厭"},{"pid":"ab3d8e04b48dd0f8afda200968a7480425e8db05","tid":893494,"uid":38569,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T17:00:45.000Z","msg":"FG啱啱出嚟 諗落忽然間跳去另一份工好似對生活好大轉變咁 不過其實成世人流流長<br />\n唔早啲變到你30歲嗰陣就冇乜本錢去試新嘢試鍾意嘅嘢由Entry做起<br />\n可能轉轉吓間公司啲人夾 啲工作又冇咁無聊會有返啲動力呢<br />\n<br />\n利申FG做咗三個月嘢"},{"pid":"8fe7811a8f2be049c8ab2772f942576522f6f708","tid":893494,"uid":172936,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T23:24:05.000Z","msg":"本身都幾鍾意份工嘅工作內容，因為興趣所在<br />\n雖然有時有啲job 嘅性質會無聊<br />\n但總體算Ok<br />\n<br />\n自己做出嚟嘅嘢會通街擺/派<br />\n諗到呢點就更加有動力做好佢<br />\n有時weekend會實地睇吓自己有份做出嚟嘅成果<br />\n跟住禮拜一就會充滿幹勁咁去翻工"},{"pid":"db7ce241854a99fc96c96da95abe50d39d3b5b8a","tid":893494,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T23:31:18.000Z","msg":"試下lunch 走去做運動，做十五分鐘都好，沖個涼再返工"},{"pid":"19d316ab060a4251443c7bf309ac6e78009c172f","tid":893494,"uid":147892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fe7811a8f2be049c8ab2772f942576522f6f708","tid":893494,"uid":172936,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T23:24:05.000Z","msg":"本身都幾鍾意份工嘅工作內容，因為興趣所在<br />\n雖然有時有啲job 嘅性質會無聊<br />\n但總體算Ok<br />\n<br />\n自己做出嚟嘅嘢會通街擺/派<br />\n諗到呢點就更加有動力做好佢<br />\n有時weekend會實地睇吓自己有份做出嚟嘅成果<br />\n跟住禮拜一就會充滿幹勁咁去翻工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:08:35.000Z","msg":"羨慕巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n番工最有成就感就係睇住自己d作品比其他人欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我而家做緊個d paper work就算我draft岩晒都只不過係一份商業文件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無咩人真係會欣賞佢既價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c067c4e47c8def99e3a04225cae571dac488b982","tid":893494,"uid":172936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19d316ab060a4251443c7bf309ac6e78009c172f","tid":893494,"uid":147892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fe7811a8f2be049c8ab2772f942576522f6f708","tid":893494,"uid":172936,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T23:24:05.000Z","msg":"本身都幾鍾意份工嘅工作內容，因為興趣所在<br />\n雖然有時有啲job 嘅性質會無聊<br />\n但總體算Ok<br />\n<br />\n自己做出嚟嘅嘢會通街擺/派<br />\n諗到呢點就更加有動力做好佢<br />\n有時weekend會實地睇吓自己有份做出嚟嘅成果<br />\n跟住禮拜一就會充滿幹勁咁去翻工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:08:35.000Z","msg":"羨慕巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n番工最有成就感就係睇住自己d作品比其他人欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我而家做緊個d paper work就算我draft岩晒都只不過係一份商業文件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無咩人真係會欣賞佢既價值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:56:39.000Z","msg":"其實我都唔知我做嘅嘢係咪真係受人欣賞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  畢竟唔會有feedback<br />\n<br />\n不過自問盡咗力就得喇"},{"pid":"987c935328e21e9320ce940f49113f8e7b5c3f29","tid":893494,"uid":186087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T05:04:30.000Z","msg":"無。"},{"pid":"b24bdc7657057c6cba19c90f382cc7f67137f04b","tid":893494,"uid":14324